---
// src/pages/privacy.astro
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="AllezCrol - P-P">
    <div class="privacy-page-container">

        <header class="privacy-header">
            <h1 class="main-title">Privacy-Policy</h1>
            <p class="sub-title">Editor: AllezCrol</p>
        </header>

        <hr class="cyber-divider" />

        <main class="privacy-flex-layout">

            <section class="privacy-box" id="box-en">
                <div class="box-header">For International</div>
                <div class="box-content">
                    <p class="update-date">Last updated: May 26, 2026</p>
                    <p>Welcome to <strong>AllezCrol</strong>. We deeply respect your privacy and do not maintain any user account system or active database tracking. However, basic access details are automatically processed to ensure server uptime and performance.</p>

                    <h3>1. Information Collected Automatically</h3>
                    <p>When you visit, our hosting platform logs standard metadata, including your masked IP address, browser type, and timestamps. This data is strictly volatile and used only to power the dashboard (RESP/LOAD times) at the bottom of the layout.</p>

                    <h3>2. Cookies and Third-Party Assets</h3>
                    <p>This site itself does not inject tracking cookies. Any external asset integration—such as fonts, scripts, or embedded content—operates under its respective provider's terms. We recommend verifying their standard privacy practices independently.</p>

                    <h3>3. Security Architecture</h3>
                    <p>All data transit is enforced through HTTPS encryption protocol layers to mitigate interception vectors.</p>
                    <h3>4. No Data to Export or Delete</h3>
                    <p>Cuz we collect absolutely nothing linked to ur real-world id, we literally have no database to search through if u ask us to "delete ur data." ur privacy isn't justa promise here-it's physically built into the lack of code.</p>

                    <h3>5. More Info</h3>
                    <p>
                        AllezCrol's Emails: yunya_2024@foxmail.com // 896722563@qq.com.<br/>
                        Users can currently contact me through these 2 email addresses, but make sure not to disturb normal life.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="resize-handle" data-target="box-en"></div>
            </section>

            <section class="privacy-box" id="box-zh">
                <div class="box-header">For Chinese</div>
                <div class="box-content">
                    <p class="update-date">最近更新日期：2026年5月26日</p>
                    <p>欢迎访问 <strong>AllezCrol</strong>。本站属于完全纯净的独立博客，<strong>不设任何账户注册或登录系统</strong>，亦不主动存储任何用户的个人保密私隐。</p>

                    <h3>一、 自动生成的日志数据</h3>
                    <p>当您接入本站时，托管平台会自动记录基础网络日志（包括您的 IP 地址、浏览器指纹、访问时间等）。这些数据仅在内存中临时用于计算并驱动您在页脚看到的 RESP 与 LOAD 实时毫秒耗时，绝不进行归档或二次商业分析。</p>

                    <h3>二、 关于 Cookie 与第三方集成</h3>
                    <p>本站源码不包含任何主动跟踪的 Cookie 行为。如后续集成评论、网站流量统计等外部插件，这些服务将遵循其原厂隐私合规条例。我们已对静态资源（如字体文件）实现了本地化部署，以杜绝第三方不必要的数据回传。</p>

                    <h3>三、 政策变更与合规</h3>
                    <p>本条款随网站架构演进可能随时发生微调。如有任何异议，均可通过公开开源渠道或邮件联系所有权人：AllezCrol。</p>
                    <h3>四、 无导入，无删除</h3>
                    <p>因为我们完全不收集与您真实身份相关的任何信息，如果您要求我们“删除您的数据”，我们实际上没有数据库可以搜索。您的隐私不仅仅是一个承诺——它实际上体现在代码的缺失中。</p>

                    <h3>五、 其余信息</h3>
                    <p>
                        AllezCrol的邮箱： yunya_2024@foxmail.com // 896722563@qq.com.<br/>
                        用户可以通过该两个邮箱地址联系本人，但注意确保不要打扰到本人的正常生活。
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="resize-handle" data-target="box-zh"></div>
            </section>

        </main>

        <hr class="cyber-divider" />

    </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style lang="scss">
  // ==========================================
  // 📺 CRT 老式显示器显示效果全局控制台
  // ==========================================
  $color-red-main: #ff3b30;
  $color-tier-days: #ff3b30;
  $color-cyan: #00ffcc;
  $color-text-dim: #777777;
  $color-border: #333333;
  $color-box-bg: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.5);

  // 1. 全局干扰核心关键帧
  @keyframes scanline-move {
    0% { transform: translateY(-100%); }
    100% { transform: translateY(1000%); }
  }

  @keyframes text-flicker {
    0% { opacity: 0.98; text-shadow: 0 0 4px rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
    50% { opacity: 1; text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255,255,255,0.5), 1px 0 1px rgba(255,0,0,0.2); }
    100% { opacity: 0.99; text-shadow: 0 0 3px rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
  }

  @keyframes title-flicker {
    0% { text-shadow: 0 0 4px rgba($color-red-main, 0.4); }
    50% { text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba($color-red-main, 0.8), -1px 0 2px rgba(0,255,200,0.4); }
    100% { text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba($color-red-main, 0.4); }
  }

  @keyframes screen-vignette {
    0% { box-shadow: inset 0 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); }
    50% { box-shadow: inset 0 0 35px rgba(15,15,15,0.9); }
    100% { box-shadow: inset 0 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); }
  }

  // 2. 基础页面包裹
  .privacy-page-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 40px auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
    font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
  }

  // 🔥 修复：强制对齐并拉回主标题悬浮放大变深红特效
  .privacy-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 25px;

    .main-title {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      color: #000000;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      display: inline-block;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275), color 0.2s ease;

      // 悬停动画正式复活
      &:hover {
        color: $color-red-main !important;
        transform: scale(1.15);
      }
    }

    .sub-title {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: $color-text-dim;
      margin-top: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
  }

  // 极客分割线
  .cyber-divider {
    border: 0;
    border-top: 1px dashed $color-border;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  // 🔥 修复：双语独立框架排版（拉开 25px 独立间距，防死粘）
  .privacy-flex-layout {
    display: flex;
    gap: 25px;            // 核心：强制撑开左右两个显示器的物理距离
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin: 30px 0;
    width: 100%;

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      flex-direction: column; // 手机端变上下列
    }
  }

  // 3. 独立 CRT 电视机框架样式
  .privacy-box {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    width: 100%;
    height: 450px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid $color-border;

    // 📺 黑色背景 + 灰色扫描线
    background: #000000;
    background-image: linear-gradient(
            rgba(18, 18, 18, 1) 50%,
            rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.4) 50%
    );
    background-size: 100% 4px;
    animation: screen-vignette 4s infinite;

    // 自上而下强干扰线条
    &::before {
      content: " ";
      display: block;
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; bottom: 0; right: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(
              rgba(18, 16, 16, 0) 0%,
              rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 10%,
              rgba(18, 16, 16, 0) 20%
      );
      width: 100%;
      height: 10%;
      z-index: 10;
      pointer-events: none;
      animation: scanline-move 6s linear infinite;
    }

    // 内部独立标题槽
    .box-header {
      background: #0d0d0d;
      border-bottom: 1px solid $color-border;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      z-index: 2;
    }

    // 内部文本槽
    .box-content {
      padding: 20px;
      overflow-y: auto;
      flex: 1;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      z-index: 2;

      color: #ffffff;
      animation: text-flicker 0.15s infinite;

      .update-date {
        color: $color-text-dim;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-shadow: none;
      }

      // 内标题全变红色发光干扰
      h3 {
        color: $color-tier-days;
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-top: 22px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding-bottom: 4px;
        animation: title-flicker 0.25s infinite;
      }

      p {
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      strong {
        color: #ffffff;
        text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      }
    }

    // 手柄
    .resize-handle {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 8px;
      background: transparent;
      cursor: ns-resize;
      z-index: 20;
      transition: background 0.2s ease;

      &:hover {
        background: rgba($color-red-main, 0.2);
      }
    }

    &.is-resizing {
      border-color: $color-red-main;
    }
  }
</style>

<script is:inline>
    (function() {
        const handles = document.querySelectorAll('.resize-handle');

        handles.forEach(handle => {
            handle.addEventListener('mousedown', function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();

                const targetId = this.getAttribute('data-target');
                const box = document.getElementById(targetId);
                const content = box.querySelector('.box-content');

                // 1. 动态边界精算
                // 最小高度：标题栏高度 + 正文开头一部分（取200px保证不会完全缩瞎）
                const minHeight = 180;
                // 最大高度：整个内容彻底铺开的真实高度 + 标题栏高度
                const maxHeight = content.scrollHeight + 40;

                const startHeight = box.clientHeight;
                const startY = e.clientY;

                box.classList.add('is-resizing');

                function onMouseMove(moveEvent) {
                    const deltaY = moveEvent.clientY - startY;
                    let newHeight = startHeight + deltaY;

                    // 2. 严格锁死上下限边界
                    if (newHeight < minHeight) {
                        newHeight = minHeight;
                    }
                    if (newHeight > maxHeight) {
                        newHeight = maxHeight;
                    }

                    box.style.height = `${newHeight}px`;
                }

                function onMouseUp() {
                    box.classList.remove('is-resizing');
                    window.removeEventListener('mousemove', onMouseMove);
                    window.removeEventListener('mouseup', onMouseUp);
                }

                // 绑定到全局 window 上，防止鼠标划得太快滑出容器导致断联
                window.addEventListener('mousemove', onMouseMove);
                window.addEventListener('mouseup', onMouseUp);
            });
        });
    })();
</script>
